&lt;li&gt;Implement and manage the PRM platform end-to-end, including deal registration workflows, partner pipeline visibility, rebate/entitlement tracking, partner newsletters, and SFDC integration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive evolution of Partner Program Operations— scaling MDF, building partner tiering frameworks, and providing partners with improved visibility into entitlements, pipeline, and earnings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with GTM Systems and Deal Desk to manage and optimize the partner price book in our quoting-to-cash process, streamline the closing process for partner-led deals, and improve the overall partner deal experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Partnerships team to identify and implement optimizations across partner workflows, including lead funnel management, onboarding, incentive programs, and partner agreement processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with internal stakeholders in Marketing, Finance, and Business Operations to ensure data integrity for partner tracking and reporting on leads, campaigns, and opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
